"executed since the last `commit()` or `rollback()` and `~ConnectionInfo."
"transaction_status` is `~pq.TransactionStatus.IDLE`)."
msgstr ""

#: ../../../api/connections.rst:387
msgid ""
"Furthermore, it is an error to call `!commit()` or `!rollback()` within the "
"TPC transaction: in this case a `ProgrammingError` is raised."
msgstr ""

#: ../../../api/connections.rst:391
