"name resolution blocks, unless the `!hostaddr` parameter is specified, or "
"the `~psycopg._dns.resolve_hostaddr_async()` function is used."
msgstr ""

#: ../../../api/connections.rst:506
msgid ""
"You can use ``async with`` to close the connection automatically when the "
"block is exited, but be careful about the async quirkness: see :ref:`async-"
"with` for details."
msgstr ""

